r number of days where\ntemperatures were between 4{\\deg}C and 10{\\deg}C. Results obtained from this\nstudy may be used to guide the reinforcement of biosecurity and surveillance\nstrategies at farms and areas within the distance threshold of PRRSV positive\nfarms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2023 22:12:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 14:39:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-09"}
